You will be served by professionals in their field - competent and sociable croupiers. And if you liked the dealer, then you have the opportunity to express gratitude with a reward in the form of a tip. The most active players of the live casino section also regularly receive bonuses.

And a special software reads the image of the cards, the ball in the roulette after the spins, automatically calculating your bets.
